&lt;p&gt;Working with a vision of being “the hospital of choice for our local community, providing first class hospital-based services to our patients”, the post holder will work with the Divisional Management Team and manage the day-to day delivery of outpatient services. Specifically, the post holder will be responsible for providing operational and management support as part of the management team to ensure that the outpatient department achieves its performance objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
